import React from 'react'

import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from './html/home_page/Home'
import { Header } from './Components/Registration/index'
import {
    LivingPlaceRegistrationSomeQuestions,
    LivingPlaceRegistrationComplexInformations,
    LivingPlaceRegistrationResidenceInformations,
    LivingPlaceRegistrationFloorplanInformations,
    LivingPlaceRegistrationRoomsInformations
} from './Pages/Registration/index'
import {
    LivingPlaceRegistrationStep6,
    LivingPlaceRegistrationSendDatas
} from './Validations/Registration/index'

import Tab from './Tests/Tab'

import SearchResult from './html/search_result/SearchResult'
import VheDetails from './html/vhe_details/VheDetails'

import './App.scss'

const App = () => {

  console.log(window.innerHeight)

  return (
    <>
      <Router>
        <Header />
          <Routes>
            <Route path='/home' element={<Home />} />

            <Route path='/living_place_registration/some_questions' element={<LivingPlaceRegistrationSomeQuestions />} />
            <Route path='/living_place_registration/complex_informations' element={<LivingPlaceRegistrationComplexInformations />} />
            <Route path='/living_place_registration/residence_informations' element={<LivingPlaceRegistrationResidenceInformations />} />
            <Route path='/living_place_registration/floorplan_informations' element={<LivingPlaceRegistrationFloorplanInformations />} />
            <Route path='/living_place_registration/rooms_informations' element={<LivingPlaceRegistrationRoomsInformations />} />
            <Route path='/living_place_registration/step6' element={<LivingPlaceRegistrationStep6 />} />
            <Route path='/living_place_registration/send_datas' element={<LivingPlaceRegistrationSendDatas />} />
          </Routes>
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
